Module chav1961.purelib
Package chav1961.purelib.basic.interfaces

Interface CharStreamPrinter<T>

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.io.Closeable, java.io.Flushable
All Known Implementing Classes:
AsmWriter, InOutGrowableCharArray, PrintStreamWrapper, PrintWriterWrapper, Term
public interface CharStreamPrinter<T>
extends java.io.Flushable, java.io.Closeable

This interface contains useful methods to print different content to character stream. It's functionality is similar to standard Java PrintStream and PrintWriter interface. This interface is oriented to use in the chained operations

Since:
0.0.3
Author:
Alexander Chernomyrdin aka chav1961
See Also:
PrintStream, PrintWriter
